The Saar-Radweg starts at the Canal de la Marne au Rhin near Gondrexange and ends at the Mosel-Radweg near Konz. It follows the Canal des Houillères de la Sarre and the Sarre.

This relation is only the relation for the Saar-Radweg / Vallée de Sarre. There are no signs of EuroVelo 5
